{"tid":970730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保方首度萌起退休念頭是因為遇見他……","createTime":"2019-01-06T05:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T08:37:43.000Z","uid":1121,"like":196,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"6f94d62f8dccd957533375e36a60f54a0a7e1404","tid":970730,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"PSG門將保方接受Eurosport訪問時，談及自己首次萌起退休的念頭，是因為他在球場上遇見了一個人&mdash;&mdash;自己舊隊友基艾沙（Erico Chiesa）的兒子Federico。<br />\n<br />\n保方說：「我之前可能沒有過多考慮退休的問題，直到我在球場上遇到了舊隊友（Erico）基艾沙的兒子（Federico Chiesa），那時我意識到自己可能要退役了&hellip;&hellip;」小基艾沙生於1997年10月，當時保方和他的父親在帕爾馬還是隊友。及至2016年8月費倫天拿與祖雲達斯對壘，18歲的小基艾沙和保方相遇了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.sportsyeah.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/F8003A22-1B29-45F8-BA13-5D5E5EBCE409.jpeg?w=1296\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.sportsyeah.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FF8003A22-1B29-45F8-BA13-5D5E5EBCE409.jpeg%3Fw%3D1296&h=98bbaacb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我第一次面對小基艾沙時，我真的有一些迷失方向。」保方說：「這是我第一次和舊隊友的兒子比賽，我感覺自己應該退役了&hellip;&hellip;不過，我現在接受了這一切，我覺得這也是上天賜予你的一份不錯的禮物，這是值得欣喜的事。」<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，保方在PSG還遇到了自己另一位舊隊友杜林的兒子Marcus。兩人在去年8月PSG對甘崗的比賽中相遇，並交換了球衣。"},{"pid":"c569ed1a0e02f6fc22f07bc59895d4dc7ee1afb3","tid":970730,"uid":1121,"like":278,"dislike":2,"score":276,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"幾時到同舊隊友個孫同場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461c4a4a6c7913b151b24dd26fdbc42e5468fc34","tid":970730,"uid":125380,"like":82,"dislike":97,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢一早應該要收山啦 好似d老屎忽賴死唔走"},{"pid":"82426cd4f282d3ed361a37feb7f5d9f0acc63e79","tid":970730,"uid":59283,"like":17,"dislike":35,"score":-18,"citedBy":